metadata.name: Oneiric Opalescence
metadata.description:
Swirling myriad vibrant tendrils surrounding shapes that are both strange and familiar evokes a vision of a psychedelic dream of an extravagant carnival. Take a break from everyday life and lose yourself for a while exploring and discovering faces, animals, and surprises in this saturated somnial landscape.

This piece is a 1/10 edition intricately created by Maneki Neko. It began as many text-to-image conversations with an AI to produce raw imagery which was curated to fit with a vision and meticulously collaged to produce a finished piece with a coherent color scheme, expression of a theme, and packed full of elaborate detail.
